CIE Automotive Seen Doubling Profit in 3 Years, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-03-16T06:35:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/cie-automotive-seen-doubling-profit-in-3-years-expansion-says.html
Spanish car parts maker  CIE
Automotive SA (CIE)  is likely to double its profit and reach sales of
2 billion euros ($2.8 billion) in three years, according to
Chairman Antonio Pradera and Chief Executive Officer Ignacio
Martin,  Expansion  reported. 